{"type":"message","id":"b71def41","parentId":"a55de56f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:12:58.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sir is saying the gateway can start itself now (no longer needs the watchdog script), and telling me not to run the gateway-watchdog.ps1 script anymore. The watchdog was causing issues - it was repeatedly trying to restart the gateway and failing, which created a cascade of problems.\n\nI should acknowledge this and maybe note that the watchdog script was actually the source of the restart loop problem - it was killing the gateway process and then failing to restart it properly.","thinkingSignature":"e88fbdf688bb79243a1aa82f13901cc6ecb4b67be120960a7e4031342a835f57"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n明白了，watchdog 脚本本身就是造成重启循环的罪魁祸首——它 kill 掉网关后自己启动失败，然后循环重试。网关现在能自己站稳了，不用再跑那个脚本了。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":159,"output":144,"cacheRead":50608,"cacheWrite":8338,"totalTokens":59249,"cost":{"input":0.0000636,"output":0.000216,"cacheRead":0.00202432,"cacheWrite":0.0012507,"total":0.00355462}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773922369854}}
