{"type":"message","id":"2fb24836","parentId":"641b7f93","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:14:51.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway is running (RPC probe: ok, Listening: 127.0.0.1:18789). But Sir says it's not working again. The issue is the same as before - the watchdog script is probably still running and causing restart loops. But Sir asked me not to run the watchdog script.\n\nWait, but the status shows the gateway is currently running. Maybe Sir is testing if it stays up without the watchdog script. The watchdog script is a separate process that monitors and kills the gateway. Since Sir asked me not to run the watchdog script anymore, the gateway should be able to stay up on its own now.\n\nBut the status says \"RPC probe: ok\" and \"Listening\", so it seems to be running right now. \n\nThe status output is showing it's actually running fine at the moment, so I'm not sure why Sir said it's not working again - maybe they experienced a brief hiccup that's already resolved, or there's something else going on that the status isn't capturing.","thinkingSignature":"640348594cc29925bb669377c0cc7ca68f106c7292f484a578c6d60a0d40b711"},{"type":"text","text":"网关现在其实在跑（RPC probe: ok，端口 18789 监听中）。你当时感觉不行了是正好撞在哪个时间点上？是 webchat 这边显示断了，还是飞书那边不通？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":21265,"output":246,"cacheRead":38726,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60237,"cost":{"input":0.008506000000000001,"output":0.000369,"cacheRead":0.00154904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01042404}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773922481507}}
