{"type":"message","id":"ef16f832","parentId":"aff3e27a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:19:58.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - the scheduled task is **disabled** (`<Enabled>false</Enabled>`). The task calls `gateway.cmd` which itself calls `node ... openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789`. So the `gateway` subcommand IS there in the .cmd file, but the task is disabled.\n\nWait, but the doctor said \"Service command does not include the gateway subcommand\". Let me re-read the doctor's output more carefully...\n\nActually, looking at the gateway.cmd again:\n```\n\"C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node.exe\" C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\dist\\index.js gateway --port 18789\n\n\n```\n\nThis looks correct. The issue might be that the doctor is reading a cached version of the service config, or it's checking something else. But the real situation is clear: the scheduled task exists, the .cmd file has the correct command, but the task is disabled. Meanwhile the gateway is running because something else started it at some point, and the watchdog script was what kept it alive before. The user told me not to run the watchdog anymore. Now they're asking why they can't start me — meaning when they try to interact with the gateway, it's not responding.\n\nBut I can still respond right now through webchat, so maybe they're referring to the Feishu channel or the desktop control UI not working. Let me just explain the situation: the gateway.cmd is configured correctly with the `gateway` subcommand, the scheduled task is disabled so it won't auto-start, but the gateway is currently running from some other process. If they want the scheduled task to work as a proper startup mechanism, they'd need to enable it.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"e4af84398cbc27f9b3690db2c3498fa4573fd3de2812694fd8728252764e57a4"},{"type":"text","text":"找到真相了——计划任务是** disabled 状态**（`<Enabled>false</Enabled>`），所以根本不会自动启动。网关现在能跑是因为之前某次手动启动的残留进程加 watchdog 脚本在撑着。\n\n`gateway.cmd` 里的命令本身是对的（有 `gateway` 子命令），但计划任务被禁用了。有两个选择：\n\n1. **启用计划任务** — `schtasks /Change /TN \"OpenClaw Gateway\" /Enable`（但需要解决命令问题，因为它没有 `gateway` 子命令时会直接退出）\n2. **不用计划任务，改用 `openclaw gateway start`** — 这次会真正启动服务\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27600,"output":487,"cacheRead":38726,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66813,"cost":{"input":0.011040000000000001,"output":0.0007305,"cacheRead":0.00154904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013319540000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773922784813}}
