{"type":"message","id":"96c4e3c5","parentId":"b431c3b8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:33:52.047Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me summarize the status of all agents:\n\n1. **main** - Heartbeat: 30m, Active session (34% tokens)\n2. **coder** - Heartbeat: disabled\n3. **newsai** - Heartbeat: disabled, has an active session from 2m ago (38k tokens)\n4. **pm** - Heartbeat: disabled\n5. **finance** - Heartbeat: disabled\n\nAll agents are running on MiniMax-M2.5 except main which uses MiniMax-M2.7.\n\nThe Feishu channel is OK with 5 accounts configured.","thinkingSignature":"912e050d12db4d097591193a30133ebedd65656f78b28569488560ad4255603a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n| Agent | Heartbeat | 状态 | Session |\n|-------|-----------|------|---------|\n| **main** | 30分钟 | ✅ 活跃 | 当前 session，34% tokens |\n| **coder** | 已禁用 | 💤 空闲 | 无 |\n| **newsai** | 已禁用 | 💤 空闲 | 2分钟前有 session |\n| **pm** | 已禁用 | 💤 空闲 | 无 |\n| **finance** | 已禁用 | 💤 空闲 | 无 |\n\n飞书频道：✅ OK（5个账户都配置好了）\n\n只有 **newsai** 最近跑过，其他三个 agent（coder/pm/finance）都处于完全空闲状态。要启用它们的 heartbeat 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32439,"output":282,"cacheRead":38726,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71447,"cost":{"input":0.0129756,"output":0.00042300000000000004,"cacheRead":0.00154904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01494764}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773923619129}}
