{"type":"message","id":"9f1c462c","parentId":"abf0be8f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:34:21.800Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why the agents that haven't started aren't starting. They want to know why coders, pm, finance etc. aren't running. The answer is that these agents have their heartbeats disabled - they only run when triggered by a Feishu message or some other event. They're not continuously running like the main agent.\n\nWait, actually thinking about this more carefully - in OpenClaw, agents can be \"spawned\" or they can be persistent. The heartbeat being disabled means they don't have a periodic check-in mechanism. But actually, in OpenClaw's architecture, all agents are basically the same - they run as sessions. When a message comes in on a channel bound to a specific agent, that agent's session is spawned to handle it.\n\n\nSo the real issue is that those other agents aren't continuously running processes waiting to be triggered - they only activate when a message arrives on their bound channel. Since their heartbeats are disabled and they lack a cron-based awakening mechanism, they just sit dormant until someone sends them a message through their respective channel.","thinkingSignature":"fcb5f645c094304613681c95440e908cd447fb57e97b80d1ad785bc7c925ed14"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n这些 agent 不是\"启动着待机\"的服务进程——它们是按需唤醒的。只有当消息发到它们对应的飞书账户时，它们才会被激活。\n\n所以：\n- **没收到消息** → agent 就一直不运行，不消耗资源\n- **收到消息** → 自动拉起对应的 agent session 处理\n\n如果你想让某个 agent 定期主动工作（比如定时新闻摘要），需要给它配置 heartbeat 或 cron 任务。目前只有 main 有 30 分钟 heartbeat，其他都禁用了。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":159,"output":322,"cacheRead":69087,"cacheWrite":2018,"totalTokens":71586,"cost":{"input":0.0000636,"output":0.00048300000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00276348,"cacheWrite":0.0003027,"total":0.00361278}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773923646580}}
{"type":"message","id":"a03e384a","parentId":"9f1c462c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:34:55.592Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-19 20:34 GMT+8] 没有启动的agent 呢"}],"timestamp":1773923695590}}
{"type":"message","id":"262712a0","parentId":"a03e384a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:35:09.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about agents that are \"not started\" - meaning the background services/tasks. They want to know about running services for each agent.\n\nI think the user might be asking about the \"Node service\" mentioned in the status output - \"Node service: Scheduled Task not installed\". Or they might be asking about what processes are running for each agent.\n\nActually, looking at the status output again:\n- Gateway service: Scheduled Task installed\n- Node service: Scheduled Task not installed\n\nThe \"Node service\" is different from the Gateway service. The node service might be the per-agent task service. But it says \"Scheduled Task not installed\" for the Node service.\n \nSo each agent doesn't run as a separate persistent process - they're activated on demand when messages arrive through the Feishu channel. The Gateway service handles the main websocket gateway, but there's no equivalent scheduled task running for individual agents to keep them alive between messages. a persistent background service at the OS level.\n\nI think what the user might be asking is: why aren't there OS-level services running for each agent? And the answer is: OpenClaw's architecture doesn't work that way. Each agent runs within the main gateway process, and they're activated on-demand through the session mechanism. There's no need for separate OS-level services for each agent.\n\nBut wait - the \"Node service: Scheduled Task not installed\" in the status might be what the user is referring to. This could be the per-agent background service that the user expected to exist.\n\nLet me just explain the architecture simply.","thinkingSignature":"4e1e919d0642231c6081be0e73071b01e9a3f956d8a19d32f5879ff3ffa394f4"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\nOpenClaw 里每个 agent 不是独立的系统服务——它们都运行在同一个 Gateway 进程里，通过会话（session）被激活。没有\"待机的 agent 进程\"这种东西。\n\n你说的\"没有启动的 agent\"是指哪个？是想让某个 agent 像服务一样一直在后台跑着吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":141,"output":379,"cacheRead":71293,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71813,"cost":{"input":0.0000564,"output":0.0005685,"cacheRead":0.00285172,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034766199999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773923695591}}
