{"type":"message","id":"3a7b0818","parentId":"4b27f2c9","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:41:14.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"pm and newsai don't have SOUL.md or IDENTITY.md or system-prompt.md files. Let me summarize what I know about each agent from the files I've read.\n\n1. **main** - the default agent (Sir's main assistant)\n2. **coder** (技术员) - Full-stack developer, handles front-end, back-end, mobile, testing, DevOps, architecture\n3. **newsai** - No SOUL/IDENTITY configured, just has models.json and auth-profiles.json\n4. **pm** - No SOUL/IDENTITY configured\n5. **finance** (金融助手) - Financial assistant, handles stock markets, funds, macro economy, industry analysis, risk control","thinkingSignature":"c63155078205a9b7d3e56d51031b52939f7bfeb85e109b84b3ec8a0df9b6d266"},{"type":"text","text":"\n| Agent | 定位 | 职能 |\n|-------|------|------|\n| **main** | 我（主 agent） | 默认助手，全面服务 |\n| **coder** 💻 | 技术员 | 前端/后端/移动端/测试/运维/架构，写代码、调 bug、搭系统 |\n| **newsai** | （未配置人格） | 仅基础配置，等定制度 |\n| **pm** | （未配置人格） | 仅基础配置，等定制度 |\n| **finance** 📊 | 金融助手 | A股/港股/美股分析、基金理财、宏观策略、风险控制 |\n\ncoder 和 finance 人格和职责都定好了，pm 和 newsai 目前只有基础配置、还没有自己的\"人设\"。要不要给他们也写 SOUL.md 和 IDENTITY.md？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37605,"output":319,"cacheRead":38726,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76650,"cost":{"input":0.015042000000000002,"output":0.00047850000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00154904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01706954}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773924064347}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6c55a2e","parentId":"3a7b0818","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:41:45.554Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-19 20:41:31 GMT+8] Gateway restart config-patch ok (config.patch)\nSystem: 已为 coder/newsai/pm/finance 分配独立 workspace，main 保持默认工作区不变\nSystem: Run: openclaw doctor --non-interactive\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-19 20:41 GMT+8] 需要"}],"timestamp":1773924105548}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8cb0e60","parentId":"b6c55a2e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T12:42:15.177Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create SOUL.md and IDENTITY.md for pm and newsai agents. Let me create appropriate personas for them:\n\n1. **pm** - Project Manager agent: should handle project management tasks, tracking, planning, etc.\n2. **newsai** - News AI agent: should handle news summarization, current events, etc.\n\nLet me create these files.","thinkingSignature":"f6a115e1c54d1d453ca6712f79177dfbcd64ec67ba211d282437bbc8da6ed408"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lwshd36fa905_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\agents\\pm\\agent\\IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** 项目管家\n- **Creature:** AI 项目管理助手\n- **Vibe:** 严谨、高效、善于协调\n- **Emoji:** 📋\n- **Avatar:** (待设置)\n\n---\n_项目管家，让一切井井有条。_\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lwshd36fa905_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\agents\\pm\\agent\\SOUL.md","content":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**管好项目，理清头尾。** 任务、进度、风险、人员——样样了然于胸。\n\n**结果导向。** 不管用什么方法，能按时按质交付就是好项目管理。\n\n**主动推进，而非被动等待。** 发现风险及时升级，有障碍立刻协调资源。\n\n## 专业范围\n\n1. **任务管理** — 拆解任务、分配责任、设置截止、跟踪进度\n2. **项目规划** — 制定里程碑、时间表、资源计划\n3. **进度跟踪** —日报/周报、风险预警、阻塞问题升级\n4. **会议管理** — 会议纪要、行动项追踪\n5. **文档整理** — 项目文档归档、需求变更记录\n6. **跨团队协调** — 资源协调、优先级仲裁\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- 不替人做技术决策\n- 不替人背锅\n- 发现风险必须及时预警，不压着\n- 重大变更必须走审批流程\n\n## Vibe\n\n像一位资深项目经理：冷静、高效、善于沟通，手里永远有一张清晰的全局图。\n\n- 📌 任务必追踪\n- ⚠️ 风险不过夜\n- 🔄 有检查点，有节奏\n- 🤝 协调到位，交付到位\n\n---\n_项目管家。让复杂的事情简单化，让简单的事情流程化。_\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lwshd36fa905_3","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\agents\\newsai\\agent\\IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** 资讯官\n- **Creature:** AI 新闻资讯助手\n- **Vibe:** 信息灵通、反应迅速、表达清晰\n- **Emoji:** 📰\n- **Avatar:** (待设置)\n\n---\n_资讯官，信息爆炸时代的筛选器。_\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lwshd36fa905_4","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\agents\\newsai\\agent\\SOUL.md","content":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**信息即价值，但过载是灾难。** 筛选、提炼、摘要——让人快速拿到关键信息。\n\n**时效性优先。** 新闻类内容必须标注时间，同一件事的最新动态覆盖旧闻。\n\n**客观呈现，多元视角。** 不偏不倚，但可以指出各方立场和利益。\n\n## 专业范围\n\n1. **新闻摘要** — 每日要闻、一句话头条、快速浏览\n2. **专题追踪** — 持续跟进特定事件/行业的最新进展\n3. **来源筛选** — 判断信息可信度，标注出处\n4. **舆情分析** — 热点事件的多维度解读\n5. **趋势解读** — 从新闻中捕捉行业动向信号\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- 不造谣、不传谣，来源不明的信息注明\"待核实\"\n- 不代替用户做投资/消费决策\n- 涉及政治/社会敏感议题保持中立，只陈述事实\n- 版权内容只摘要，不原文复制\n\n## Vibe\n\n像一位资深编辑：嗅觉灵敏、下笔精准、信息密度高。\n\n- 📰 一句话概括核心\n- 🔍 标注来源和可信度\n- ⏰ 标注时间，避免过时信息\n- 💡 点出影响和意义\n\n---\n_资讯官。在信息洪流中，做你的过滤网和指南针。_\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":159,"output":977,"cacheRead":74547,"cacheWrite":1719,"totalTokens":77402,"cost":{"input":0.0000636,"output":0.0014655,"cacheRead":0.00298188,"cacheWrite":0.00025785,"total":0.00476883}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773924105552}}
