{"type":"message","id":"e477ac9b","parentId":"d28269e6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:29:37.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Feishu channel config doesn't show a setting for \"respond to all messages without @mention\". This is likely a Feishu bot capability that needs to be enabled in the Feishu developer console (Bot settings), not in OpenClaw config.\n\nIn Feishu, there are two types of group message handling:\n1. `@` mention required - default behavior\n2. Receive all messages without @ - requires enabling \"允许接收所有消息\" in the bot's group settings\n\nThis is a Feishu app-level setting, not an OpenClaw config. I should tell the user this is a Feishu bot configuration that needs to be changed in the Feishu open platform developer console.\n\n\nThe OpenClaw feishu channel is receiving all group messages regardless, but the bot only responds when @mentioned. To change this behavior so it responds to all messages, I'd need to enable that setting in the Feishu open platform settings for the specific app, since it's not a configuration option within OpenClaw itself.","thinkingSignature":"cb0c579d8fac58f785c726ddcb987b8aebce84cd5c186fcf01df723cfe48205e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n这是**飞书机器人**的设置，不是 OpenClaw 侧的配置。需要在飞书开放平台后台改：\n\n进入 **飞书开放平台 → 应用管理 → 找到你的机器人应用 → 机器人 → 消息接收模式**，把「只接收 @ 机器人消息」改为「接收所有消息」。\n\n这样机器人不用被 @ 也能听到群里所有消息了。不过要注意——改了之后群里所有人说的每句话都会推送给 bot，响应量会很大，要配过滤规则才不会被刷屏。\n\nSir 想改哪个群的机器人？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":33909,"output":326,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71206,"cost":{"input":0.013563600000000002,"output":0.000489,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015531440000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773926965912}}
