{"type":"message","id":"50d83343","parentId":"c23d2c7a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T13:57:37.184Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't see a specific \"agent-to-agent\" configuration option in the OpenClaw config. Agent-to-agent communication is done through the `sessions_send` tool. Each agent (when active) can use `sessions_send` to send messages to other agents.\n\nBut for agents to proactively communicate with each other without user involvement, we'd need something like:\n1. Each agent having a cron job that periodically triggers\n2. Or some event-based trigger system\n\nActually, looking at the OpenClaw docs, agents can use the `sessions_send` tool to send messages to other agents' sessions. But the agents need to be active (have a running session) for this to work.\n\nWait - maybe the user is asking about setting up Feishu group chat configurations where each agent is assigned to a different group, and they can communicate with each other through those groups? Or maybe they want to set up a system where when one agent finishes a task, it notifies another agent?\n \nI'm realizing there's no built-in \"agent-to-agent mode\" in OpenClaw—agents communicate through Feishu as a transport layer, so they'd need to be mentionable in groups or configured as cross-agent bridges. But thinking about this differently, the user might want a \"supervisor\" pattern where main monitors other agents' activities and can delegate tasks to them, or they want all agents reachable via a unified Feishu account. I should ask what the actual goal is rather than guessing at architectures.","thinkingSignature":"809b2e02b7c5f099e496c5aa7bb22a37aff8a52193efa4160a7f04fbbcf64dbd"},{"type":"text","text":"目前 OpenClaw 没有一个专门的 \"agent to agent\" 开关来让各 agent 自动互相调用。各 agent 之间的通信有几种方式：\n\n1. **通过我（main）转发** — 类似刚才让金融虾分析股票，我作为中枢转发任务和结果\n2. **各 agent 通过飞书互相 @** — 每个 agent 的飞书账户在群里互相 @ 对方\n3. **定时触发 + sessions_send** — 给某个 agent 配置 cron，定期向其他 agent 发消息\n\n不过说实话，agent to agent 在 OpenClaw 里没有现成的\"一键互联\"配置，更多是**通过我作为中枢来协调**。Sir 想要的是哪种场景？比如：\n- 咨询虾看到新闻 → 自动转发给金融虾分析？\n- 项目虾的任务状态 → 自动同步给 main？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39711,"output":470,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77152,"cost":{"input":0.0158844,"output":0.000705,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01806824}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773928642595}}
