{"type":"message","id":"ca0f5e7d","parentId":"52872b24","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:31:07.397Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The newsai subagent successfully completed but couldn't find Sir's Feishu ID to send the message. The news is about 岚图汽车 listing on HKEX. Let me provide the user's Feishu ID from the message context - it's `ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389`. But actually, the subagent tried to use feishu_im_user_message without having the user's open_id. The problem is the newsai agent doesn't have the OAuth for the user's account to send messages.\n\nActually, the real issue is that the newsai subagent was trying to use `feishu_im_user_message` (as the user) to send to Sir, but it didn't have authorization to do so. \n\nThe feishu_im_user_message tool requires user OAuth, and the subagent session doesn't have that access. I should send this news to Sir directly from main since I have the context, and let them know the subagent's limitation.","thinkingSignature":"dceaa1fe438b30c4e1a3ecf3fbab6770360717102cf84441b3a1150a0eca5a5a"},{"type":"text","text":"新闻虾任务完成了，但遇到了一个问题——它没有权限以 Sir 的身份发消息，所以推送失败了。\n\n今日新闻内容：**岚图汽车今日正式在港交所上市，成为\"央国企高端新能源汽车第一股\"，武汉东湖上空飞艇助阵。**\n\n这条我帮 Sir 推送。同时说一下根本原因：新闻虾是子 agent，没有 Sir 的飞书发消息权限。需要的话可以让我（主 agent）来转发，或者给新闻虾配置 OAuth 授权才能独立推送。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":306,"cacheRead":22443,"cacheWrite":73882,"totalTokens":96778,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000459,"cacheRead":0.0008977200000000001,"cacheWrite":0.0110823,"total":0.01249782}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773930652541}}
