{"type":"message","id":"a7b93c5d","parentId":"99218d76","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:38:23.905Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sir is asking if the message was sent. I tried to revoke the OAuth but the system needs to re-authorize. I haven't actually sent a message yet. Let me try to send a test message to see if the OAuth re-authorization was triggered.","thinkingSignature":"bfe6401ee62e196b355ff35ac23a6b39ae7569dfabf98f3f86418c61a9bad6ab"},{"type":"text","text":"还没发，刚才只是在撤销授权。现在试试以 Sir 身份发消息，看能不能触发重新授权：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gnds6w7vw6xv_1","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"open_id","receive_id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121121340f36ca389","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"Sir，这是来自主 agent 的测试消息。\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":178,"cacheRead":97188,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":98253,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000267,"cacheRead":0.00388752,"cacheWrite":0.000111,"total":0.00432432}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931092388}}
{"type":"message","id":"03c4953d","parentId":"a7b93c5d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:38:25.436Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gnds6w7vw6xv_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_message","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"awaiting_app_authorization\": true,\n  \"message\": \"已向用户发送授权引导卡片，等待用户完成授权操作。请告知用户：按照卡片提示完成授权，完成后系统将自动重试之前的操作。请等待用户完成卡片操作，不要建议其他替代方案。\",\n  \"missing_scopes\": [\n    \"im:message.send_as_user\"\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"awaiting_app_authorization":true,"message":"已向用户发送授权引导卡片，等待用户完成授权操作。请告知用户：按照卡片提示完成授权，完成后系统将自动重试之前的操作。请等待用户完成卡片操作，不要建议其他替代方案。","missing_scopes":["im:message.send_as_user"]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931105407}}
{"type":"message","id":"fde4be6e","parentId":"03c4953d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:38:31.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system is showing an \"awaiting_app_authorization\" message. This means the OAuth authorization needs to be done by Sir. A card was sent to Sir with a link to authorize. Sir needs to follow the card prompts to complete the authorization.\n\nBut wait - looking at the context, the feishu_im_user_message tool is trying to send on behalf of the user, but the system is showing this authorization card message. This means the OAuth was revoked and now needs to be re-authorized.\n\nI should tell Sir that an authorization card has been sent to them in Feishu and they need to follow the prompts to authorize.","thinkingSignature":"f9863a1ef9aaaf548b5c9f9720e7d89e4132f555a4d60993689031e2d59497ea"},{"type":"text","text":"触发了！飞书里应该收到了一张**授权引导卡片**，Sir 需要按卡片里的提示完成授权操作。授权完成后我就能以 Sir 的身份发消息了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61374,"output":168,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98513,"cost":{"input":0.0245496,"output":0.000252,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02628044}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931105438}}
