{"type":"message","id":"e427552a","parentId":"f0c8a53a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:10.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OAuth issue again - need to re-authenticate. Actually wait, I already sent messages with user identity earlier. Let me try a different approach - let me use the feishu_im_user_get_messages to find the SUP group chat_id. But I need the chat_id first.\n\nActually, let me try to search for the group. But the search requires OAuth too. \n\nHmm, maybe I should try to get the list of chats the user is in. But the search_messages tool requires OAuth. \n\nActually the issue is that I just successfully sent messages using feishu_im_user_message with chat_id oc_8929608dc38ef89c99b606322db21a85, so the OAuth is working. \n\nThe problem seems to be with the search tool itself - let me try searching with a simpler query instead of the SUP group name.","thinkingSignature":"24177f6e4b31b621f44f6f823830037ab49eac54fcd14d16fc20977258753642"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4tn4zj118w4i_1","name":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","arguments":{"query":"群","chat_type":"group"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64891,"output":216,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102078,"cost":{"input":0.0259564,"output":0.000324,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02775924}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931383291}}
