{"type":"message","id":"63e5b01b","parentId":"4ec1f25a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:19.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The OAuth seems to have been revoked or expired. But earlier I was able to send messages successfully. Let me check the current OAuth status. Actually, the issue might be that each tool call with user identity requires re-authentication or there's a session issue.\n\nWait - actually looking back, the `feishu_im_user_message` worked fine (returned message_id), but `feishu_im_user_search_messages` is showing \"awaiting_authorization\". This might be because the OAuth token for search is different from the one for messaging, or the token expired.\n\nLet me ask Sir to re-authorize again, or alternatively, I can try to get the group info differently. \n\nI'm realizing that each Feishu API scope might need its own OAuth token, and the `im:message:send_as_user` scope I used before doesn't necessarily cover search operations. The simplest fix is to just ask Sir for the SUP group chat_id directly, since I've already confirmed messaging works.","thinkingSignature":"40fa81eadfb1dd750b211bba72e2447fb62ca0ac9cc60497c5c90eae418db178"},{"type":"text","text":"搜索群需要重新授权。Sir 能把 SUP 群的 `chat_id`（群 ID，通常是 `oc_xxx` 格式）告诉我吗？或者在群里发一条消息，我来获取 chat_id。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65166,"output":244,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102381,"cost":{"input":0.026066400000000003,"output":0.000366,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02791124}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931390561}}
