{"type":"message","id":"8327dedb","parentId":"a8caee6b","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:43:57.543Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zn05rbu26495_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b58b5dca0b3dd650bed00d65\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"应用权限已开通\\\">\\nApp permissions ready. Starting user authorization...\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:51:51+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 @新闻虾 @技术虾 @金融虾  你们用自己anget名称介绍自己\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:51:40+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_2\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb\",\n          \"name\": \"新闻虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_3\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n          \"name\": \"技术虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_4\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n          \"name\": \"金融虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b66c7e4b4b31e3257156cb57\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"授权成功\\\">\\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\\n\\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:56:32+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 我给你打开权限了你看看\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:56:13+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b41ecf4a4c2d4a37775c444a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir您好！看起来您@的是 **新闻虾**、**技术虾**、**金融虾** 这几位，但我不是它们哦～\\n我是 **PM**（当前在这个群聊里响应的是我）。\\n您是想让我帮忙联系其他几位，还是有其他事情需要处理？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:49:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 好了\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:16:11+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 @新闻虾 @技术虾 @金融虾 介绍一下自己\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:57:51+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_2\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb\",\n          \"name\": \"新闻虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_3\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n          \"name\": \"技术虾\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_4\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n          \"name\": \"金融虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b753544a4b264825ed48655e\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，要我能查到 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾** 的信息，需要：\\n1. **把它们加入企业通讯录** - 确保它们是你们企业的正式成员/联系人\\n2. **调整您的可见范围** - 在飞书管理后台，把这几个账号的部门/人员放到您的\\\"通讯录可见范围\\\"内\\n3. **或者用应用身份** - 如果这些是机器人应用，需要开放应用通讯录权限\\n\\n---\\n\\n最简单的方式：问一下公司IT，这几个账号是否在企业通讯录里？如果在，让我获得查看权限就行 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:01:51+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b75f788b4b4c606638aaa1e2\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b54ac20a0b3ca66e930d0e28\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 要给开什么权限\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:52:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b107050a0c3272e02f7572af\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"啊，这样啊 😅 那可能是我的配置问题，确实不太行...\\nSir那这个问题先放一边，您还有其他需要帮忙的吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:11:07+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b10c17ca4b348e03b5f1c9ec\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b3c3ebca0b49f3cd087d3f9c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"还是不行 😅\\n这个权限是加在**应用**上的，但我调用的是**用户身份API**（用您的授权token），还是会受限于您自己的通讯录可见范围...\\n这个问题有点复杂，可能需要用应用身份而不是用户身份来查。\\n您先忙，不用管这个了～让我先记下来，后续看看怎么解决 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:16:31+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b67a5dd38b290ec2cf46c270\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 好了\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:56:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b546c60a8c492f8db2aa828f\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我是**项目虾** 🦐\\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\\n（@新闻虾 和 @金融虾 也在群里，他们分别是新闻和金融领域的助手～）\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:52:58+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b1ffcc8b4b28b6d418e6814f\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 你需要的权限给我\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:07:31+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b064da8b4b267e7602995396\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"还是搜不到 😅 可能需要**稍等片刻**让权限生效，或者您可以再确认下：\\n1. 是否把它们加入了您的**通讯录可见范围**？\\n2. 还是只加到了**应用权限**里？（应用权限和用户可见范围是两回事）\\n您先忙，我等会再试～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:05:12+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b09e5f54cb3cf0f58d02fc5b\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b643130a8b3300bc38370dc1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，抱歉！授权后还是查不到 😢\\n搜索**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**都显示**没有结果**。这说明：\\n- 它们可能不是您企业通讯录中的正式用户\\n- 或者它们属于其他组织/部门，您这边没有访问权限\\n如果您知道它们的**真实姓名**或**邮箱**，我可以换个方式再试试～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:57:19+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b2d2198a8b4b6d3856de0f6a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card>\\nSir，找到原因了！\\n\\n看配置，我（PM）和其他几个机器人用的是**不同的飞书应用**：\\n\\n| 机器人 | App ID |\\n|------|------|\\n| 新闻虾 (newsai) | cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb |\\n| 技术虾 (coder) | cli_a930e5a091badbd7 |\\n| 金融虾 (finance) | cli_a93109b4a1791bca |\\n| 我 (PM) | cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2 |\\n|  |  |问题是**我的应用**（pm）可能没有开通通讯录权限，而其他几个应用已经有了。\\n\\n**解决方法**：在飞书开放平台，给 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2** 这个应用也开通通讯录权限 🦐\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:12:31+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b11210c88b28d1febfa741c2\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b63962ca4b337e3b094a5162\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我是**项目虾** 🦐\\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\\n@新闻虾 🦐 是新闻资讯小助手\\n@金融虾 🦐 是金融分析小助手\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:57:57+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b5f1f7ca4b396c3af3211ad9\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"授权成功！你好，王杭 👋\\n我是 **财务虾** 🦐\\n我的专长是帮你处理财务相关的事务：\\n- 📊 整理和分析财务数据\\n- 📁 管理财务文件（表格、凭证等）\\n- 📅 安排财务会议和日程\\n- 🔍 搜索财务相关信息\\n有什么财务上的事情需要帮忙随时叫我！\\n至于你 @的其他三位小伙伴（项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾），他们可能还没上线，下次你可以直接喊他们出来自我介绍~ 😄\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:50:37+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b75f788b4b4c606638aaa1e2\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 要怎么样你能获取\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:01:39+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b55dadca8b21025d8b20c7fa\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"根据之前的错误提示，需要您在飞书管理后台调整**通讯录权限**：\\n**方式一：调整组织架构可见范围**\\n让管理员把\\\"新闻虾\\\"、\\\"技术虾\\\"、\\\"金融虾\\\"这几位的部门/人员放到您的**可见范围**内。\\n**方式二：应用权限配置**\\n如果是用应用身份调用，需要管理员给应用开放**通讯录权限**（读取成员信息）。\\n\\n---\\n\\n简单说：就是您的飞书账号需要能\\\"看到\\\"那几位，才能查到它们的信息 🦐\\n需要我帮您进一步操作吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:53:05+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b54ac20a0b3ca66e930d0e28\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b5eb450b4b2722a35a0b5a2c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"授权成功\\\">\\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\\n\\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:50:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b0122dca0c39d0a35f4b4af3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"还是不行 😅 权限可能需要时间同步，或者设置方式不太对。\\nSir您先忙，不用管这个了～还有其他我能帮到的吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:07:11+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b01cdd0bcb377c976fa31bd0\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b5e1aa4acb2d1da628a0badc\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"嗨！我是 **财务虾** 🦐\\n我的专长是帮你管理财务相关的事情：\\n- 📊 记账、整理财务数据\\n- 📁 管理财务文件（表格、文档等）\\n- 📅 处理财务日程和会议\\n- 🔍 搜索和分析财务信息\\n不过我需要获得授权才能查看你的信息和帮你办事。点击消息中的链接完成授权后，我就能更好地帮你啦！\\n至于项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾他们三位，得等他们自己出来介绍咯~ 😄\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:50:21+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b712b78a0b219f5785dbca50\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 现在可以了吗\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:02:54+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b1875e0a4b3711b978ea2215\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 获取通讯录权限范围：与可用人员范围保持一致\\n\\n与可用人员范围保持一致\\n这些都有啊\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:08:59+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b406510a0c42973f37483acc\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"大家好！我是 **NewsAI** 🗞️\\n我是你们的新闻助手，负责追踪资讯、整理动态。有什么新闻、简讯或者信息汇总的需求随时叫我！\\n顺便问一下：需要我帮你关注哪方面的资讯？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:49:46+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b11210c88b28d1febfa741c2\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 你检查\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:11:26+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b0f0c74a8b263ec9b7ec8aa3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"还是不行 😢 依然没有权限/搜不到\\nSir您可以先忙别的，这个问题先放一边～还有其他需要我帮忙的吗？\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:03:24+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b712b78a0b219f5785dbca50\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b09e5f54cb3cf0f58d02fc5b\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 好了\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:04:50+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b0cb100b0b39ce41c80f45dc\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"需要什么权限@项目虾\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:03:35+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b60f9c0a0b10fab4a7491309\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir again～\\n我确实没办法获取 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾** 的信息 😅\\n可能它们是外部联系人或者没有录入通讯录。\\n要不您直接 @它们，让它们自己介绍一下？它们要是能响应，应该会自己说话的～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:58:11+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b1bb06ca0b36700e6b44c9a8\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"获取通讯录权限范围：与可用人员范围保持一致\\n\\n与可用人员范围保持一致\\n这些都有啊\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:08:39+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b01cdd0bcb377c976fa31bd0\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 你看我又更新了权限\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:06:56+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b26d458a0b32aaaaa58cf82a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，在飞书开放平台开通通讯录权限：\\n1. 打开 [https://open.feishu.cn/app](https://open.feishu.cn/app)\\n2. 找到应用 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2**（或者搜\\\"PM\\\"）\\n3. 点击进入 → **权限管理**\\n4. 搜索\\\"通讯录\\\" → 开通以下权限：\\n  - **获取成员基本信息**\\n  - **获取成员组织架构信息**\\n  - **通过手机号或邮箱查询用户**\\n5. **创建应用版本** → **提交审核** → **发布**\\n开通后告诉我，我再试一下 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:13:37+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b596b14a0b337b13043c1be2\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"interactive\",\n      \"content\": \"<card title=\\\"授权成功\\\">\\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\\n\\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\\n</card>\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:52:10+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b587854b4b372cc4d8070ce1\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我是**项目虾** 🦐\\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\\n（另外两个小伙伴 **新闻虾** 和 **金融虾** 也在这里，他们分别是新闻和金融领域的助手～）\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a930e5a091badbd7\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:51:55+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b588208a8b3f71e0a4c24d4b\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"哈哈，我是 **财务虾** 🦐 啦！\\n至于项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾他们三个——他们是这个群里的其他 AI 助手，不是我这个\\\"虾\\\"呀。要他们自我介绍，得看他们有没有在这个群里上线并获得授权咯~\\n你可以直接 @他们试试，看他们会不会冒泡！😄\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:51:49+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b6356f4a8b3b8c93b21fcd78\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"看起来项目虾已经介绍过自己啦！从上面的记录看：\\n**项目虾** 🦐 - 擅长编程和开发\\n至于 **新闻虾** 和 **技术虾**～他们可能还没进群或者没授权，暂时不出来 😄\\n有需要随时叫我这个财务虾～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a93109b4a1791bca\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:58:01+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b0dde4910c3921ff723c8db8\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，需要以下权限：\\n1. **通讯录权限** - 让您的账号能查看**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**的信息\\n  - 在飞书管理后台 → 通讯录权限 → 把它们加入您的\\\"可见范围\\\"\\n2. **或者搜索权限** - 能通过姓名/邮箱搜索到这几个账号\\n\\n---\\n\\n简单理解：就是您需要在飞书里\\\"能看到\\\"它们，我现在才能查到 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:03:45+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b0cb100b0b39ce41c80f45dc\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b66b2e8acb287c7402ddbef3\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，抱歉！试了几种方式，依然显示**没有权限** 😢\\n可能还需要您在飞书管理后台进一步确认：\\n1. **组织架构权限** - 确保您的账号能\\\"看到\\\"这几个机器人（新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾）\\n2. **应用权限** - 如果这些是机器人应用，需要在应用配置里开放通讯录权限\\n您可以联系公司IT/管理员帮忙看下具体是哪里限制了 🙏\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:56:40+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b58f3a4b0b21ae9e30bbed14\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我是 **项目虾** 🦐\\n专注新闻资讯与项目动态，帮你追踪热点、整理信息。需要什么新闻或者资料，随时问我！\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:51:48+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"怎么开通@项目虾\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:13:30+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b10c17ca4b348e03b5f1c9ec\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 就你一个不行 其他的都可以\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:10:56+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b658dd8a8b3f8a723c5ad8ec\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"好的，Sir！🦐 有什么需要随时叫我～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:57:24+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b67a5dd38b290ec2cf46c270\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b576874b4b315636ed9dfded\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"我是项目虾 🦐\\n\\n我擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:52:42+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b63bcacb0b241add96fd7d70\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"我是 **项目虾** 🦐\\n专注新闻资讯与项目动态，帮你追踪热点、整理信息。有需要随时叫我！\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:57:59+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b596a04a0b228ea663f9229a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，抱歉！我目前无法直接获取 **新闻虾**、**技术虾**、**金融虾** 这几位的详细信息（权限限制）。\\n如果您想了解它们的功能，我可以帮您：\\n1. **搜索飞书文档** 看看有没有相关的介绍\\n2. **查看知识库** 是否有它们的能力说明\\n或者，您可以单独@它们试试看？也许它们自己能回复～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T20:52:10+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b1f3618a8b3697ce49221d57\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，要让我能查到那几个账号的信息，您需要在飞书管理后台设置：\\n**路径：飞书管理后台 → 通讯录 → 通讯录权限管理 → 设置用户的通讯录可见范围**\\n然后把 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**（或者它们所在的部门）加入到您的**可见范围**里。\\n\\n---\\n\\n或者如果这些是**机器人应用**，需要在：\\n**飞书管理后台 → 应用管理 → 找到这几个应用 → 开放通讯录权限**\\n您看看是哪种情况？🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:07:43+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b1ffcc8b4b28b6d418e6814f\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b197d6ca8b3fb533c00517bf\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，既然您权限已经有了，那问题可能是：\\n**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾 可能不是你们企业的正式成员**（比如是外部联系人、机器人账号等），所以即使用户有权限也搜不到。\\n这种情况我也帮不了忙了 😅\\n不过它们既然能在这个群里，应该能自己回复。您直接 @它们，让它们自己介绍一下得了～\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:09:15+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b1875e0a4b3711b978ea2215\",\n      \"chat_id\": \"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589\",\n      \"chat_type\": \"group\",\n      \"chat_name\": \"全局\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"page_token\": \"0ba3d83b030ad1c9964d3e53555584f6ec6911a70f88bc51e406e660770b\"\n}"}],"details":{"messages":[{"message_id":"om_x100b548b58b5dca0b3dd650bed00d65","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card title=\"应用权限已开通\">\nApp permissions ready. Starting user authorization...\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:51:51+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 @新闻虾 @技术虾 @金融虾  你们用自己anget名称介绍自己","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:51:40+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"},{"key":"@_user_2","id":"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb","name":"新闻虾"},{"key":"@_user_3","id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","name":"技术虾"},{"key":"@_user_4","id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","name":"金融虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b66c7e4b4b31e3257156cb57","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card title=\"授权成功\">\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\n\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:56:32+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 我给你打开权限了你看看","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:56:13+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b41ecf4a4c2d4a37775c444a","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir您好！看起来您@的是 **新闻虾**、**技术虾**、**金融虾** 这几位，但我不是它们哦～\n我是 **PM**（当前在这个群聊里响应的是我）。\n您是想让我帮忙联系其他几位，还是有其他事情需要处理？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:49:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 好了","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:16:11+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 @新闻虾 @技术虾 @金融虾 介绍一下自己","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:57:51+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"},{"key":"@_user_2","id":"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb","name":"新闻虾"},{"key":"@_user_3","id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","name":"技术虾"},{"key":"@_user_4","id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","name":"金融虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b753544a4b264825ed48655e","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，要我能查到 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾** 的信息，需要：\n1. **把它们加入企业通讯录** - 确保它们是你们企业的正式成员/联系人\n2. **调整您的可见范围** - 在飞书管理后台，把这几个账号的部门/人员放到您的\"通讯录可见范围\"内\n3. **或者用应用身份** - 如果这些是机器人应用，需要开放应用通讯录权限\n\n---\n\n最简单的方式：问一下公司IT，这几个账号是否在企业通讯录里？如果在，让我获得查看权限就行 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:01:51+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b75f788b4b4c606638aaa1e2","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b54ac20a0b3ca66e930d0e28","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 要给开什么权限","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:52:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b107050a0c3272e02f7572af","msg_type":"post","content":"啊，这样啊 😅 那可能是我的配置问题，确实不太行...\nSir那这个问题先放一边，您还有其他需要帮忙的吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:11:07+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b10c17ca4b348e03b5f1c9ec","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b3c3ebca0b49f3cd087d3f9c","msg_type":"post","content":"还是不行 😅\n这个权限是加在**应用**上的，但我调用的是**用户身份API**（用您的授权token），还是会受限于您自己的通讯录可见范围...\n这个问题有点复杂，可能需要用应用身份而不是用户身份来查。\n您先忙，不用管这个了～让我先记下来，后续看看怎么解决 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:16:31+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b67a5dd38b290ec2cf46c270","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 好了","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:56:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b546c60a8c492f8db2aa828f","msg_type":"post","content":"我是**项目虾** 🦐\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\n（@新闻虾 和 @金融虾 也在群里，他们分别是新闻和金融领域的助手～）","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:52:58+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b1ffcc8b4b28b6d418e6814f","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 你需要的权限给我","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:07:31+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b064da8b4b267e7602995396","msg_type":"post","content":"还是搜不到 😅 可能需要**稍等片刻**让权限生效，或者您可以再确认下：\n1. 是否把它们加入了您的**通讯录可见范围**？\n2. 还是只加到了**应用权限**里？（应用权限和用户可见范围是两回事）\n您先忙，我等会再试～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:05:12+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b09e5f54cb3cf0f58d02fc5b","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b643130a8b3300bc38370dc1","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，抱歉！授权后还是查不到 😢\n搜索**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**都显示**没有结果**。这说明：\n- 它们可能不是您企业通讯录中的正式用户\n- 或者它们属于其他组织/部门，您这边没有访问权限\n如果您知道它们的**真实姓名**或**邮箱**，我可以换个方式再试试～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:57:19+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b2d2198a8b4b6d3856de0f6a","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card>\nSir，找到原因了！\n\n看配置，我（PM）和其他几个机器人用的是**不同的飞书应用**：\n\n| 机器人 | App ID |\n|------|------|\n| 新闻虾 (newsai) | cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb |\n| 技术虾 (coder) | cli_a930e5a091badbd7 |\n| 金融虾 (finance) | cli_a93109b4a1791bca |\n| 我 (PM) | cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2 |\n|  |  |问题是**我的应用**（pm）可能没有开通通讯录权限，而其他几个应用已经有了。\n\n**解决方法**：在飞书开放平台，给 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2** 这个应用也开通通讯录权限 🦐\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:12:31+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b11210c88b28d1febfa741c2","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b63962ca4b337e3b094a5162","msg_type":"post","content":"我是**项目虾** 🦐\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\n@新闻虾 🦐 是新闻资讯小助手\n@金融虾 🦐 是金融分析小助手","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:57:57+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b5f1f7ca4b396c3af3211ad9","msg_type":"post","content":"授权成功！你好，王杭 👋\n我是 **财务虾** 🦐\n我的专长是帮你处理财务相关的事务：\n- 📊 整理和分析财务数据\n- 📁 管理财务文件（表格、凭证等）\n- 📅 安排财务会议和日程\n- 🔍 搜索财务相关信息\n有什么财务上的事情需要帮忙随时叫我！\n至于你 @的其他三位小伙伴（项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾），他们可能还没上线，下次你可以直接喊他们出来自我介绍~ 😄","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:50:37+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b75f788b4b4c606638aaa1e2","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 要怎么样你能获取","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:01:39+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b55dadca8b21025d8b20c7fa","msg_type":"post","content":"根据之前的错误提示，需要您在飞书管理后台调整**通讯录权限**：\n**方式一：调整组织架构可见范围**\n让管理员把\"新闻虾\"、\"技术虾\"、\"金融虾\"这几位的部门/人员放到您的**可见范围**内。\n**方式二：应用权限配置**\n如果是用应用身份调用，需要管理员给应用开放**通讯录权限**（读取成员信息）。\n\n---\n\n简单说：就是您的飞书账号需要能\"看到\"那几位，才能查到它们的信息 🦐\n需要我帮您进一步操作吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:53:05+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b54ac20a0b3ca66e930d0e28","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b5eb450b4b2722a35a0b5a2c","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card title=\"授权成功\">\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\n\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:50:15+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b0122dca0c39d0a35f4b4af3","msg_type":"post","content":"还是不行 😅 权限可能需要时间同步，或者设置方式不太对。\nSir您先忙，不用管这个了～还有其他我能帮到的吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:07:11+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b01cdd0bcb377c976fa31bd0","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b5e1aa4acb2d1da628a0badc","msg_type":"post","content":"嗨！我是 **财务虾** 🦐\n我的专长是帮你管理财务相关的事情：\n- 📊 记账、整理财务数据\n- 📁 管理财务文件（表格、文档等）\n- 📅 处理财务日程和会议\n- 🔍 搜索和分析财务信息\n不过我需要获得授权才能查看你的信息和帮你办事。点击消息中的链接完成授权后，我就能更好地帮你啦！\n至于项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾他们三位，得等他们自己出来介绍咯~ 😄","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:50:21+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b712b78a0b219f5785dbca50","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 现在可以了吗","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:02:54+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b1875e0a4b3711b978ea2215","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 获取通讯录权限范围：与可用人员范围保持一致\n\n与可用人员范围保持一致\n这些都有啊","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:08:59+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b406510a0c42973f37483acc","msg_type":"post","content":"大家好！我是 **NewsAI** 🗞️\n我是你们的新闻助手，负责追踪资讯、整理动态。有什么新闻、简讯或者信息汇总的需求随时叫我！\n顺便问一下：需要我帮你关注哪方面的资讯？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:49:46+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b40ef08a8b4a48dbc70ea063","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b11210c88b28d1febfa741c2","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 你检查","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:11:26+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b0f0c74a8b263ec9b7ec8aa3","msg_type":"post","content":"还是不行 😢 依然没有权限/搜不到\nSir您可以先忙别的，这个问题先放一边～还有其他需要我帮忙的吗？","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:03:24+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b712b78a0b219f5785dbca50","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b09e5f54cb3cf0f58d02fc5b","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 好了","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:04:50+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b0cb100b0b39ce41c80f45dc","msg_type":"text","content":"需要什么权限@项目虾","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:03:35+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b60f9c0a0b10fab4a7491309","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir again～\n我确实没办法获取 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾** 的信息 😅\n可能它们是外部联系人或者没有录入通讯录。\n要不您直接 @它们，让它们自己介绍一下？它们要是能响应，应该会自己说话的～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:58:11+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b1bb06ca0b36700e6b44c9a8","msg_type":"text","content":"获取通讯录权限范围：与可用人员范围保持一致\n\n与可用人员范围保持一致\n这些都有啊","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:08:39+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b01cdd0bcb377c976fa31bd0","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 你看我又更新了权限","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:06:56+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b26d458a0b32aaaaa58cf82a","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，在飞书开放平台开通通讯录权限：\n1. 打开 [https://open.feishu.cn/app](https://open.feishu.cn/app)\n2. 找到应用 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2**（或者搜\"PM\"）\n3. 点击进入 → **权限管理**\n4. 搜索\"通讯录\" → 开通以下权限：\n  - **获取成员基本信息**\n  - **获取成员组织架构信息**\n  - **通过手机号或邮箱查询用户**\n5. **创建应用版本** → **提交审核** → **发布**\n开通后告诉我，我再试一下 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:13:37+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b596b14a0b337b13043c1be2","msg_type":"interactive","content":"<card title=\"授权成功\">\nFeishu account authorized. Continuing with your request.\n\nLet me know if you ever need to revoke the permissions.\n</card>","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:52:10+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b587854b4b372cc4d8070ce1","msg_type":"post","content":"我是**项目虾** 🦐\n擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。\n（另外两个小伙伴 **新闻虾** 和 **金融虾** 也在这里，他们分别是新闻和金融领域的助手～）","sender":{"id":"cli_a930e5a091badbd7","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:51:55+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b588208a8b3f71e0a4c24d4b","msg_type":"post","content":"哈哈，我是 **财务虾** 🦐 啦！\n至于项目虾、新闻虾、技术虾他们三个——他们是这个群里的其他 AI 助手，不是我这个\"虾\"呀。要他们自我介绍，得看他们有没有在这个群里上线并获得授权咯~\n你可以直接 @他们试试，看他们会不会冒泡！😄","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:51:49+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b6356f4a8b3b8c93b21fcd78","msg_type":"post","content":"看起来项目虾已经介绍过自己啦！从上面的记录看：\n**项目虾** 🦐 - 擅长编程和开发\n至于 **新闻虾** 和 **技术虾**～他们可能还没进群或者没授权，暂时不出来 😄\n有需要随时叫我这个财务虾～","sender":{"id":"cli_a93109b4a1791bca","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:58:01+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b0dde4910c3921ff723c8db8","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，需要以下权限：\n1. **通讯录权限** - 让您的账号能查看**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**的信息\n  - 在飞书管理后台 → 通讯录权限 → 把它们加入您的\"可见范围\"\n2. **或者搜索权限** - 能通过姓名/邮箱搜索到这几个账号\n\n---\n\n简单理解：就是您需要在飞书里\"能看到\"它们，我现在才能查到 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:03:45+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b0cb100b0b39ce41c80f45dc","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b66b2e8acb287c7402ddbef3","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，抱歉！试了几种方式，依然显示**没有权限** 😢\n可能还需要您在飞书管理后台进一步确认：\n1. **组织架构权限** - 确保您的账号能\"看到\"这几个机器人（新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾）\n2. **应用权限** - 如果这些是机器人应用，需要在应用配置里开放通讯录权限\n您可以联系公司IT/管理员帮忙看下具体是哪里限制了 🙏","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:56:40+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b681808a4b273162732a6a27","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b58f3a4b0b21ae9e30bbed14","msg_type":"post","content":"我是 **项目虾** 🦐\n专注新闻资讯与项目动态，帮你追踪热点、整理信息。需要什么新闻或者资料，随时问我！","sender":{"id":"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:51:48+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52","msg_type":"text","content":"怎么开通@项目虾","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:13:30+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b10c17ca4b348e03b5f1c9ec","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 就你一个不行 其他的都可以","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:10:56+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","name":"项目虾"}],"chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b658dd8a8b3f8a723c5ad8ec","msg_type":"post","content":"好的，Sir！🦐 有什么需要随时叫我～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:57:24+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b67a5dd38b290ec2cf46c270","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b576874b4b315636ed9dfded","msg_type":"text","content":"我是项目虾 🦐\n\n我擅长编程和开发，主要帮你写代码、管文件、跑命令这些技术活。","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:52:42+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b63bcacb0b241add96fd7d70","msg_type":"post","content":"我是 **项目虾** 🦐\n专注新闻资讯与项目动态，帮你追踪热点、整理信息。有需要随时叫我！","sender":{"id":"cli_a9303f8ff2b99bdb","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:57:59+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b623644a0b3cb1ae7a07fd40","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b596a04a0b228ea663f9229a","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，抱歉！我目前无法直接获取 **新闻虾**、**技术虾**、**金融虾** 这几位的详细信息（权限限制）。\n如果您想了解它们的功能，我可以帮您：\n1. **搜索飞书文档** 看看有没有相关的介绍\n2. **查看知识库** 是否有它们的能力说明\n或者，您可以单独@它们试试看？也许它们自己能回复～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T20:52:10+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b5b0868b4b4c783d29401aae","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b1f3618a8b3697ce49221d57","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，要让我能查到那几个账号的信息，您需要在飞书管理后台设置：\n**路径：飞书管理后台 → 通讯录 → 通讯录权限管理 → 设置用户的通讯录可见范围**\n然后把 **新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾**（或者它们所在的部门）加入到您的**可见范围**里。\n\n---\n\n或者如果这些是**机器人应用**，需要在：\n**飞书管理后台 → 应用管理 → 找到这几个应用 → 开放通讯录权限**\n您看看是哪种情况？🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:07:43+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b1ffcc8b4b28b6d418e6814f","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b197d6ca8b3fb533c00517bf","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，既然您权限已经有了，那问题可能是：\n**新闻虾、技术虾、金融虾 可能不是你们企业的正式成员**（比如是外部联系人、机器人账号等），所以即使用户有权限也搜不到。\n这种情况我也帮不了忙了 😅\n不过它们既然能在这个群里，应该能自己回复。您直接 @它们，让它们自己介绍一下得了～","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:09:15+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b1875e0a4b3711b978ea2215","chat_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","chat_type":"group","chat_name":"全局"}],"has_more":true,"page_token":"0ba3d83b030ad1c9964d3e53555584f6ec6911a70f88bc51e406e660770b"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931437516}}
{"type":"message","id":"5b848dc1","parentId":"8327dedb","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:44:06.525Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the SUP group! It's called \"全局\" (quánjú) with chat_id `oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589`. Now I can send the news to that group.","thinkingSignature":"1421e34fcb546e1c1d671ec3d1fb024c1950d457e9c33e8fdc9bcd711c8bfea7"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！群名叫\"**全局**\"，chat_id 是 `oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589`。现在推送：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6szfsz8sjlvt_1","name":"feishu_im_user_message","arguments":{"action":"send","receive_id_type":"chat_id","receive_id":"oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589","msg_type":"text","content":"{\"text\":\"📰 新闻虾今日播报\\n\\n**短短48小时内，中俄战机一起升空！特朗普连忙喊话，再晚就镇不住**\\n\\n一句话：两天内中俄两国战机接连升空，节奏紧凑、指向明确，美国政策同时收紧，国际局势骤然升温。\\n\\n来源：陌上史无言（今日头条热榜）| 时间：2026年3月19日\"}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78272,"output":274,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115517,"cost":{"input":0.031308800000000005,"output":0.000411,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03319864000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773931437545}}
