{"type":"message","id":"62fd7097","parentId":"33c68416","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:45:56.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sir sent a Feishu group invite link. This is a join link for a group chat. The link format suggests it's a group join link. However, to get the chat_id of this group, I can't directly parse it from the join link. \n\nWhat I can do is ask Sir to forward a message from that group, or I can try to use the feishu API to create a chat using this link. Actually, I don't have a tool to join a group via invite link.\n\nThe best approach is to ask Sir to forward me a message from the SUP group so I can get the chat_id. Or Sir can share the chat ID directly.\n\nActually, looking at the link format: `link_token=622g307e-7c55-4034-8159-7df23A931b40` - this is a join link token. I can't directly get the chat_id from this.\n\n\nI'll need to ask Sir to either share a message from the SUP group or provide the chat ID directly.","thinkingSignature":"f5d92be51fd24efb870c31cd511094445edd88926178d428197501ef1fa25959"},{"type":"text","text":"收到了 SUP 群的邀请链接，但我没办法通过邀请链接直接获取 chat_id。\n\n最简单的办法：Sir 在 SUP 群里**随便发一条消息**（或者转发一条消息给我），我就能拿到 SUP 群的 chat_id，然后马上推送新闻。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":262,"cacheRead":115501,"cacheWrite":1859,"totalTokens":117769,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000393,"cacheRead":0.00462004,"cacheWrite":0.00027885,"total":0.005350689999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931546348}}
