{"type":"message","id":"6decd57a","parentId":"dab1a2ba","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:46:08.069Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Sir sent a message saying \"这个群\" but I still don't have the chat_id for the SUP group. Let me check if there's a way to get the chat ID from the invite link token. The link token is `622g307e-7c55-4034-8159-7df23a931b40`. I can't directly convert this to a chat_id though.\n\nWait - did Sir just forward me a message from the SUP group? Looking at the message, it says \"这个群\" (this group). But this is still from the DM channel, not from the SUP group.\n\nActually, looking more carefully - the message content is just \"这个群\" which means \"this group\". Sir might be confirming that's the group. But I still don't have the chat_id.\n \nI'm realizing the feishu_im_user_get_messages API only works for chats the user is already in, not for discovering new ones. Without the chat_id or the user's participation in the SUP group, I can't retrieve messages from it. The best path forward is to ask Sir to provide the chat_id directly from the SUP group URL, or have them add me to that group so I can access it through the API.","thinkingSignature":"4469950bd22ed68e0bafea6d6b2516cce75c29dfc6907e0bba9e0b6ee208931a"},{"type":"text","text":"我还是没有 SUP 群的 chat_id。\n\nSir 能在 SUP 群里点进群信息，把群的 **chat_id（格式是 `oc_xxx`）** 复制给我吗？一般在群信息页面最下面能看到。或者告诉我群的完整飞书链接也行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":304,"cacheRead":117285,"cacheWrite":410,"totalTokens":118146,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000456,"cacheRead":0.0046914,"cacheWrite":0.00006149999999999999,"total":0.0052677}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931557742}}
