{"type":"message","id":"79cccdc9","parentId":"47ec520d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:47:05.608Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_x55gua4e72v8_1","toolName":"feishu_im_user_get_messages","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f4f5ac7ca0c4f55a7ec4b8480\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"📰 新闻虾今日播报\\n\\n**短短48小时内，中俄战机一起升空！特朗普连忙喊话，再晚就镇不住**\\n\\n一句话：两天内中俄两国战机接连升空，节奏紧凑、指向明确，美国政策同时收紧，国际局势骤然升温。\\n\\n来源：陌上史无言（今日头条热榜）| 时间：2026年3月19日\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T22:44:06+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b3c3ebca0b49f3cd087d3f9c\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"还是不行 😅\\n这个权限是加在**应用**上的，但我调用的是**用户身份API**（用您的授权token），还是会受限于您自己的通讯录可见范围...\\n这个问题有点复杂，可能需要用应用身份而不是用户身份来查。\\n您先忙，不用管这个了～让我先记下来，后续看看怎么解决 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:16:31+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"@项目虾 好了\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:16:11+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b26d458a0b32aaaaa58cf82a\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"post\",\n      \"content\": \"Sir，在飞书开放平台开通通讯录权限：\\n1. 打开 [https://open.feishu.cn/app](https://open.feishu.cn/app)\\n2. 找到应用 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2**（或者搜\\\"PM\\\"）\\n3. 点击进入 → **权限管理**\\n4. 搜索\\\"通讯录\\\" → 开通以下权限：\\n  - **获取成员基本信息**\\n  - **获取成员组织架构信息**\\n  - **通过手机号或邮箱查询用户**\\n5. **创建应用版本** → **提交审核** → **发布**\\n开通后告诉我，我再试一下 🦐\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"app\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:13:37+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": false,\n      \"reply_to\": \"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52\",\n      \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n      \"content\": \"怎么开通@项目虾\",\n      \"sender\": {\n        \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n        \"sender_type\": \"user\",\n        \"name\": \"王杭\"\n      },\n      \"create_time\": \"2026-03-19T21:13:30+08:00\",\n      \"deleted\": false,\n      \"updated\": true,\n      \"mentions\": [\n        {\n          \"key\": \"@_user_1\",\n          \"id\": \"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d\",\n          \"name\": \"项目虾\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"has_more\": true,\n  \"page_token\": \"4cXSlmN7uFAnWWU5yfIGMOrhavdrQlEkbk0ZoG93lzEUugrFAMuuH-1aEiDUnRLqTwMND3J5GXfWciba9ExFfwFgZ9MhrW3FGq_l70dplMKekevmUx9d1YJ7NMG9NiUy\"\n}"}],"details":{"messages":[{"message_id":"om_x100b54f4f5ac7ca0c4f55a7ec4b8480","msg_type":"text","content":"📰 新闻虾今日播报\n\n**短短48小时内，中俄战机一起升空！特朗普连忙喊话，再晚就镇不住**\n\n一句话：两天内中俄两国战机接连升空，节奏紧凑、指向明确，美国政策同时收紧，国际局势骤然升温。\n\n来源：陌上史无言（今日头条热榜）| 时间：2026年3月19日","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T22:44:06+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b3c3ebca0b49f3cd087d3f9c","msg_type":"post","content":"还是不行 😅\n这个权限是加在**应用**上的，但我调用的是**用户身份API**（用您的授权token），还是会受限于您自己的通讯录可见范围...\n这个问题有点复杂，可能需要用应用身份而不是用户身份来查。\n您先忙，不用管这个了～让我先记下来，后续看看怎么解决 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:16:31+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b3f740cb0b2948b814d1ccff","msg_type":"text","content":"@项目虾 好了","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:16:11+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d","name":"项目虾"}]},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b26d458a0b32aaaaa58cf82a","msg_type":"post","content":"Sir，在飞书开放平台开通通讯录权限：\n1. 打开 [https://open.feishu.cn/app](https://open.feishu.cn/app)\n2. 找到应用 **cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2**（或者搜\"PM\"）\n3. 点击进入 → **权限管理**\n4. 搜索\"通讯录\" → 开通以下权限：\n  - **获取成员基本信息**\n  - **获取成员组织架构信息**\n  - **通过手机号或邮箱查询用户**\n5. **创建应用版本** → **提交审核** → **发布**\n开通后告诉我，我再试一下 🦐","sender":{"id":"cli_a9301e0e64f89bd2","sender_type":"app"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:13:37+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":false,"reply_to":"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52"},{"message_id":"om_x100b548b2969dca4b32e8e601255d52","msg_type":"text","content":"怎么开通@项目虾","sender":{"id":"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389","sender_type":"user","name":"王杭"},"create_time":"2026-03-19T21:13:30+08:00","deleted":false,"updated":true,"mentions":[{"key":"@_user_1","id":"ou_ff3f960fc9e2d191a7167f15349d709d","name":"项目虾"}]}],"has_more":true,"page_token":"4cXSlmN7uFAnWWU5yfIGMOrhavdrQlEkbk0ZoG93lzEUugrFAMuuH-1aEiDUnRLqTwMND3J5GXfWciba9ExFfwFgZ9MhrW3FGq_l70dplMKekevmUx9d1YJ7NMG9NiUy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773931625581}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc4edac4","parentId":"79cccdc9","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:47:22.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I only have access to the \"全局\" group (oc_ccd30fbbfa5e7a5a536f9cb018e16589). I don't see messages from the SUP group. \n\nThis is because `feishu_im_user_get_messages` with a chat_id only gets messages from a specific chat, and I don't have the SUP group's chat_id.\n\nThe message Sir sent might have been in the SUP group, but to get messages from that group, I need the chat_id first. Let me try to search for messages from the SUP group without specifying a chat_id.\n\nActually, I think the issue is that `feishu_im_user_get_messages` requires a chat_id. Without the SUP group's chat_id, I can't fetch messages from it.\n \nWait, looking at the message again - Sir mentioned someone in the SUP group sent me a message. That message would be in my chat with that person or in the SUP group chat itself. Since I don't have the SUP group's chat_id, I can't retrieve it. Sir needs to provide the SUP group's chat_id for me to access those messages.","thinkingSignature":"514882ec1d3fec463a96c8cdb42fe4782cb0a9cd26779704f213b9dd87ad395e"},{"type":"text","text":"Sir，SUP 群里的消息我没有权限直接拿到，需要 SUP 群的 chat_id 才能拉取。\n\n麻烦 Sir 这样操作：\n1. 打开飞书 SUP 群\n2. 点右上角群信息 / 群设置\n3. 滚到最下面，找到 **\"群 ID\"** 或 **\"群 chat_id\"**\n4. 把 `oc_xxx` 发给我\n\n或者直接发一条群消息，把那条消息的 **message_id** 发给我也行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82640,"output":330,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119941,"cost":{"input":0.033056,"output":0.000495,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.035029840000000007}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931625610}}
