{"type":"message","id":"bb8b3dad","parentId":"33843840","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:48:25.588Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Successfully sent to the SUP group!","thinkingSignature":"0edff8978edeb2920146ad3e8504cbb1a5d594e75c4003074f380f698037504e"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已发到 SUP 群了，Sir 刷新看看。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83283,"output":25,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120279,"cost":{"input":0.0333132,"output":0.000037500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034829540000000006}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931702691}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fddde65","parentId":"bb8b3dad","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:09.280Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-19 22:49:08 GMT+8] Feishu[main] DM | ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389 [msg:om_x100b54f480f990a0b21c9988d565f7f]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f480f990a0b21c9988d565f7f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 22:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\"\n}\n```\n\n新闻虾可以推送到那个群吗"}],"timestamp":1773931749277}}
{"type":"message","id":"64793118","parentId":"4fddde65","timestamp":"2026-03-19T14:49:23.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the newsai agent can directly push to the SUP group (oc_71ff41fed588e906f6fa6b786920c244). \n\nThe issue is that newsai is a subagent, and it doesn't have the feishu_im_user_message tool available - only main (through the feishu_im_user_ tools) has the user's OAuth authorization to send messages.\n\nHowever, with the agentToAgent feature now enabled, there might be a way for newsai to send messages through main's tools. But this would require:\n1. newsai to be able to call sessions_send or similar to relay through main\n2. Or newsai to have its own OAuth authorization\n\n\n3. Or newsai to use feishu_im_bot_image or feishu_im_user_message\n\nThe real constraint is that newsai is a subagent without feishu_im_user_message access, so it can't authenticate as the user on its own. The user is really asking whether newsai can independently push to the SUP group without going through main as a middleman.\n\nThe core issue is that newsai would need its own OAuth token for the user to send messages as them, but main currently holds the only active token. newsai might be able to use sessions_send to route through main, but that's a different mechanism than direct agent-to-agent feishu messaging.","thinkingSignature":"cd310e95fb3e1fddf3b6a7df1f6469c5b723271fdf2ccecf3910322e1cb4146b"},{"type":"text","text":"理论上可以，但需要配置。目前新闻虾（newsai）没有 `feishu_im_user_message` 工具权限，所以没办法直接推送。\n\n要让新闻虾能独立推送，需要：\n1. 给新闻虾配置**机器人应用**的 OAuth\n2. 或者通过 **agentToAgent** 让新闻虾调用 main 的工具来转发\n\n目前最实用的方案还是：**新闻虾整理内容 → 发给我 → 我推送到群**。\n\n如果想让新闻虾定时自动推送（比如每天早上 8 点），可以给它配置 cron 任务，届时自动走这个流程。要试一下吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":405,"cacheRead":119799,"cacheWrite":568,"totalTokens":120919,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.0006075,"cacheRead":0.0047919600000000005,"cacheWrite":0.0000852,"total":0.00554346}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773931749279}}
