{"type":"message","id":"54b236fe","parentId":"1f25b7c2","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:33:10.413Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-19 23:33:09 GMT+8] Feishu[main] DM | ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389 [msg:om_x100b54f53d8b08a0b3c0b2d2f73966e]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54f53d8b08a0b3c0b2d2f73966e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 23:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_c0acf4e14a9895533f121340f36ca389\"\n}\n```\n\n我现在装的这些skill会让你变得更聪明吗"}],"timestamp":1773934390409}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd3ee430","parentId":"54b236fe","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:33:27.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether the installed skills make me smarter. Let me think about this honestly.\n\nSkills are tools and capabilities that extend what I can do, not necessarily make me \"smarter\" in the raw intelligence sense. They give me:\n1. More domain-specific knowledge (finance, news, etc.)\n2. Additional tools (browser automation, desktop control, etc.)\n3. Special integrations (Feishu calendar, tasks, bitable, etc.)\n\nBut the actual \"reasoning\" is limited by the model. Let me be honest and thoughtful about this.","thinkingSignature":"c9b79d17dd7449d7bdec666492cbf58d3fc45cd1557d6b0c3d6b04af4067535d"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n说实话——**不一定**。\n\nSkills 扩展的是我能**做什么**，不是我能**多想**。\n\n- **行情、新闻、飞书工具** → 让我能做的事更多，但不提升思考深度\n- **Self-Improving + Proactivity** → 这个真的有用，帮我避免重复犯同一个错\n- **Cron + Heartbeat** → 让我更主动，不只是被动响应\n\n真正让我\"更聪明\"的是：\n1. **模型本身**（MiniMax-M2.7）\n2. **记忆和上下文管理**（MEMORY.md、自改进记录）\n3. **技能质量**（有用才装，没用不装）\n\n装太多反而有副作用：\n- 检索范围变大，拖慢响应\n- 增加误触发风险\n\n所以我建议定期审计，删掉不用的技能。要不要我给你跑一个技能清单，帮我看看哪些其实没在用？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":306,"cacheRead":22443,"cacheWrite":130058,"totalTokens":152954,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000459,"cacheRead":0.0008977200000000001,"cacheWrite":0.0195087,"total":0.02092422}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773934390412}}
