{"type":"message","id":"7d30e9d4","parentId":"5109bc71","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:35:54.037Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compile a useful summary for the user. I have:\n\n**Currently installed skills that are actually useful:**\n- self-improving ✓\n- proactivity ✓\n- memory-setup ✓\n- cron-mastery ✓\n- miliger-context-manager ✓\n- news-summary ✓\n- a-share-pro ✓\n- yanpan-finance ✓\n- browser-automation ✓\n\n**Potentially unused/less useful:**\n- skill-finder-cn (just a meta skill for finding others)\n- skill-vetter (just a vetting tool)\n- office-automation-test (test/dummy)\n- desktop-control-win (maybe useful)\n\n\n- eastmoney-stock, stock, stock-board (finance related, could overlap with yanpan-finance)\n- tushare-data (finance data)\n- multi-search-engine (useful)\n- memory-setup (already have self-improving and proactivity)\n\nFrom ClawHub, I'm seeing some promising candidates like **elite-longterm-memory** which could enhance my ability to retain and recall information long-term, and **deep-thinking** for tackling more complex reasoning tasks. There are also some interesting workflow options with **automation-workflows** and **n8n-workflow-automation**, plus **ai-researcher** and **ai-news** for specialized research capabilities.\n\nFor a finance-oriented assistant like me, the most valuable additions would be **elite-longterm-memory** for better retention of financial data and market patterns, **deep-thinking** for analyzing complex financial situations, and **ai-researcher** for gathering comprehensive financial intelligence. I should also recommend inspecting these to get a better sense of what each actually does before deciding which to install.","thinkingSignature":"0d8d1e1072bb1fbab5d6fc97c971c79e0aca34bd2615021f8b817e8b6d580fd7"},{"type":"text","text":"搜完了，结合你已装的技能，整理一下：\n\n---\n\n**已装技能审计**\n\n| 技能 | 状态 | 建议 |\n|------|------|------|\n| self-improving | ✅ 核心 | 保留 |\n| proactivity | ✅ 核心 | 保留 |\n| memory-setup | ✅ 核心 | 保留 |\n| cron-mastery | ✅ 有用 | 保留 |\n| miliger-context-manager | ✅ 有用 | 保留 |\n| news-summary | ✅ 有用 | 保留 |\n| a-share-pro | ✅ 专业 | 保留 |\n| yanpan-finance | ✅ 专业 | 保留 |\n| multi-search-engine | ✅ 有用 | 保留 |\n| browser-automation | ✅ 有用 | 保留 |\n| desktop-control-win | ⚠️ 可选 | 保留 |\n| skill-finder-cn / skill-vetter | 🔧 工具 | 保留 |\n| eastmoney-stock / stock / stock-board | ⚠️ 功能重叠 | 可考虑删除 |\n| tushare-data | ⚠️ 功能重叠 | 可考虑删除 |\n| office-automation-test | ❌ 空的 | **建议删除** |\n\n---\n\n**ClawHub 搜到值得关注的**\n\n| 技能 | 亮点 | 适合度 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 强化长期记忆，比现有 memory 更深 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **deep-thinking** | 复杂问题深度推理 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **ai-researcher** | 系统性研究分析 | ⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **adaptive-reasoning** | 自适应推理策略 | ⭐⭐ |\n| **automation-workflows** | 自动化工作流编排 | ⭐⭐ |\n\n要我帮你：\n1. **删除** eastmoney-stock / stock / stock-board / tushare-data / office-automation-test 这几个重叠/空技能？\n2. **安装** elite-longterm-memory 或 deep-thinking？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":114311,"output":736,"cacheRead":36971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152018,"cost":{"input":0.045724400000000005,"output":0.001104,"cacheRead":0.00147884,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04830724000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773934528092}}
