{"type":"message","id":"2fc0afdf","parentId":"f488484e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:52:16.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`memory-hygiene` requires LanceDB, so it has dependencies. `memory-manager` (MIT-0) and `context-budgeting` (MIT-0) seem to be the best options. \n\n`memory-manager` - compression detection, auto-snapshots, semantic search - local memory management\n`context-budgeting` - context window management, pre-compression checkpointing - very relevant for avoiding memory issues\n\nBoth are MIT-0, no external API keys needed. Let me install both since they're complementary and lightweight. Or let me ask the user which one they want.\n\nActually, the user said \"找相似的技能\" - find similar ones. Both memory-manager and context-budgeting are relevant. \n\nThese two are complementary enough that I could suggest installing both, or I could present the options and let the user choose.","thinkingSignature":"6d92a161afcf86e4cc375070b31049ca488088c000d4d280f33abb8f20cd96b9"},{"type":"text","text":"有两个无依赖的候选：\n\n- **memory-manager** — 本地记忆管理、自动快照、语义搜索（MIT-0）\n- **context-budgeting** — 上下文窗口优化、防压缩丢失、降低 token 消耗（MIT-0）\n\n两个定位不同但互补：\n- memory-manager → **记忆存储和检索**\n- context-budgeting → **上下文防丢失**\n\n建议两个都装？或者董事长选一个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117606,"output":259,"cacheRead":36964,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":154829,"cost":{"input":0.047042400000000005,"output":0.0003885,"cacheRead":0.00147856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04890946}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773935519009}}
