{"type":"message","id":"aa50324b","parentId":"382a8ccd","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:07:59.846Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a list of installed skills that make the agent \"smarter\" (i.e., reasoning, memory, research, context management, etc.). Let me list the newly installed skills that are specifically about intelligence augmentation.","thinkingSignature":"574ef6d3eb160547f4b774b9c92836d25ca141e402bdb8d7d41b17c4246bcab0"},{"type":"text","text":"已安装的智能增强类技能：\n\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| **deep-thinking** | 复杂问题深度推理框架 |\n| **ai-researcher** | 系统性深度研究与分析 |\n| **adaptive-reasoning** | 自动评估问题复杂度，动态调整推理深度 |\n| **memory-manager** | 本地记忆管理 + 自动快照 + 语义搜索 |\n| **context-budgeting** | 上下文窗口优化，防压缩丢失 |\n| **automation-workflows** | 工作流自动化设计 |\n| **super-websearch-realtime** | 实时网络搜索补充 |\n\n核心三件套（已装在 workspace 根目录的全局技能）：\n| 技能 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| **self-improving** | 自我复盘与执行质量提升 |\n| **proactivity** | 主动预测与跟进 |\n| **miliger-context-manager** | 无缝会话切换 |\n\n以上这些是真正能让我\"更聪明\"的部分。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":254,"cacheRead":144958,"cacheWrite":2087,"totalTokens":147446,"cost":{"input":0.000058800000000000006,"output":0.000381,"cacheRead":0.00579832,"cacheWrite":0.00031305,"total":0.006551169999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773936469860}}
