{"type":"message","id":"3c82ff40","parentId":"e3612744","timestamp":"2026-03-19T17:16:55.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a \"per-key concurrency\" guard for join-agent. Let me look at the join-agent function more carefully. Let me read lines around the join-agent route.","thinkingSignature":"6ca21fc956a23afc0295a7af6806d74b0786c82bae6f6977afd4db5ce40f7607"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qoi7ysj70s14_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Star-Office-UI\\backend\\app.py","offset":953,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97537,"output":99,"cacheRead":36964,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134600,"cost":{"input":0.0390148,"output":0.0001485,"cacheRead":0.00147856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04064186}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773940606036}}
{"type":"message","id":"3294df62","parentId":"3c82ff40","timestamp":"2026-03-19T17:16:55.313Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qoi7ysj70s14_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@app.route(\"/join-agent\", methods=[\"POST\"])\r\ndef join_agent():\r\n    \"\"\"Add a new agent with one-time join key validation and pending auth\"\"\"\r\n    try:\r\n        data = request.get_json()\r\n        if not isinstance(data, dict) or not data.get(\"name\"):\r\n            return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"msg\": \"请提供名字\"}), 400\r\n\r\n        name = data[\"name\"].strip()\r\n        state = data.get(\"state\", \"idle\")\r\n        detail = data.get(\"detail\", \"\")\r\n        join_key = data.get(\"joinKey\", \"\").strip()\r\n\r\n        # Normalize state early for compatibility\r\n        state = normalize_agent_state(state)\r\n\r\n        if not join_key:\r\n            return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"msg\": \"请提供接入密钥\"}), 400\r\n\r\n        keys_data = load_join_keys()\r\n        key_item = next((k for k in keys_data.get(\"keys\", []) if k.get(\"key\") == join_key), None)\r\n        if not key_item:\r\n            return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"msg\": \"接入密钥无效\"}), 403\r\n        # key 可复用：不再因为 used=true 拒绝\r\n\r\n        with join_lock:\r\n            # 在锁内重新读取，避免并发请求都基于同一旧快照通过校验\r\n            keys_data = load_join_keys()\r\n            key_item = next((k for k in keys_data.get(\"keys\", []) if k.get(\"key\") == join_key), None)\r\n            if not key_item:\r\n                return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"msg\": \"接入密钥无效\"}), 403\r\n\r\n            # Key-level expiration check\r\n            key_expires_at_str = key_item.get(\"expiresAt\")\r\n            if key_expires_at_str:\r\n                try:\r\n                    key_expires_at = datetime.fromisoformat(key_expires_at_str)\r\n                    if datetime.now() > key_expires_at:\r\n                        return jsonify({\"ok\": False, \"msg\": \"该接入密钥已过期，活动已结束 🎉\"}), 403\r\n                except Exception:\r\n                    pass\r\n\r\n            agents = load_agents_state()\r\n\r\n            # 并发上限：同一个 key “同时在线”最多 3 个。\r\n            # 在线判定：lastPushAt/updated_at 在 5 分钟内；否则视为 offline，不计入并发。\r\n            now = datetime.now()\r\n            existing = next((a for a in agents if a.get(\"name\") == name and not a.get(\"isMain\")), None)\r\n            existing_id = existing.get(\"agentId\") if existing else None\r\n\r\n            def _age_seconds(dt_str):\r\n                if not dt_str:\r\n                    return None\r\n                try:\r\n                    dt = datetime.fromisoformat(dt_str)\r\n                    return (now - dt).total_seconds()\r\n                except Exception:\r\n                    return None\r\n\r\n            # opportunistic offline marking\r\n            for a in agents:\r\n                if a.get(\"isMain\"):\r\n                    continue\r\n                if a.get(\"authStatus\") != \"approved\":\r\n                    continue\r\n                age = _age_seconds(a.get(\"lastPushAt\"))\r\n                if age is None:\r\n                    age = _age_seconds(a.get(\"updated_at\"))\r\n                if age is not None and age > 300:\r\n                    a[\"authStatus\"] = \"offline\"\r\n\r\n            max_concurrent = int(key_item.get(\"maxConcurrent\", 3))\r\n            active_count = 0\r\n            for a in agents:\r\n                if a.get(\"isMain\"):\r\n                    continue\r\n                if a.get(\"agentId\") == existing_id:\r\n                    continue\r\n                if a.get(\"joinKey\") != join_key:\r\n                    continue\r\n\n[1072 more lines in file. Use offset=1033 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773940615280}}
{"type":"message","id":"25bd7284","parentId":"3294df62","timestamp":"2026-03-19T17:17:06.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand! The join logic looks for an existing agent by NAME, not by joinKey. If an agent with the same name already exists, it reuses that agentId. That's why all my join attempts returned the same agentId - they all had different names but the backend is deduplicating by name.\n\nWait, but the names were \"技术虾\", \"新闻虾\", \"项目虾\", \"金融虾\" - these are all different. Unless... the encoding issue caused all names to be read as the same (broken) string.\n\nLooking at the agents-state.json, the registered remote agent has name \"???\" which means the name was corrupted during the JSON encoding/decoding process. \n\nSo when subsequent joins came through with garbled names, they were matching against that same corrupted name, which is why they all got assigned the same agentId. The join logic checks for existing agents by name and reuses the ID if it finds a match, but since the names were all corrupted into the same \"???\" string, every new join was treated as a duplicate of the previous one. I see the issue now - all the join requests got the same agentId because the name field was corrupted to \"???\" due to JSON encoding problems, so the backend kept reusing the same existing agent record instead of creating new ones for each join attempt. The cleanest approach is to restart the backend to clear the corrupted state, then rerun the scripts with proper character encoding so each agent gets its own distinct identity.","thinkingSignature":"92cf6a6d490102559044665fb771a3afe29fdef7d4285c00875d1e9052662a15"},{"type":"text","text":"\n找到根本原因了——后端 join 时按 name 查重，但中文 name 因为编码问题全部变成了\"???\"，导致后端认为是同一个人，每次都返回同一个 agentId，覆盖了之前的记录。\n\n解决方案：清空 agents-state.json，重启后端，然后直接用 Python 脚本启动各 agent：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cl14ca3h5f2l_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process -Name \"python\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.CommandLine -like \"*Star-Office*\" } | Stop-Process -Force; Write-Output \"Backend stopped\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":98425,"output":448,"cacheRead":36964,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135837,"cost":{"input":0.03937,"output":0.0006720000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00147856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04152056}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773940615316}}
